\f2\b History & About Kayak 
\f0\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf0 KAYAK is a travel metasearch and booking platform. It aggregates options for flights, hotels, and rental cars from multiple providers, enabling travelers to search, compare, and choose the option that best fits their needs. Your simulation will emulate these core functions- search, filter, book, bill, and analyze usage within a distributed, service-oriented architecture. 
\f0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

