\f0\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf0 In this project, you will design a 3-tier application that implements the functions of a Kayak-like travel system. You will build on the techniques used in your lab assignments to create the system. 
\f0 \

\f1 In the Kayak System, you will manage and implement different types of objects: 
\f0 \

\f1 For each type of object, you will also need to implement an associated database schema that will be responsible for representing how a given object should be stored (relational and/or document, as appropriate). 
\f0 \

\f1 Your system should be built upon a distributed architecture. You have to use REST-based web services and message queues (Kafka) as middleware technology. You will be given a great deal of \'93
