\f2\b \cf0 How to use the datasets Deals Agent (backend worker) 
\f1\b0 From Inside Airbnb pull: listing_id, date, price, availability, amenities, neighbourhood. Compute avg_30d_price, then flag deals: price \uc0\u8804  0.85 \'d7 avg_30d; mark Limited availability (<5); add simple tags (e.g., Pet-friendly, Near transit, Breakfast). From Flight Price Prediction / Expedia keep: origin, dest, airline, stops, duration, price. Use these as baselines and simulate a 
\f2\b time series 
\f1\b0 (mean-reverting price + random promo dips \uc0\u8722 10% to \u8722 25% + seats_left scarcity). }